Just four years in existence has seen Integrated Pump Rental rise to become a recognised specialist in pump rental operations in southern Africa. Lee Vine, MD of the company, says that this is not by accident but due to a strategic approach to market needs. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 8 2018. It will be published online on the 11th September 2018. You can read the full digital magazine here or subscribe here to receive a print copy